    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my left eye is looking really red and it's kinda painful too. there's a lot of weird yellow gunk/discharge when i wake up. i've been staring at my laptop for like 12 hours a day lately so i'm guessing it's just really bad dry eyes? should i just get some lubricating eye drops from the pharmacy and see if that helps?",
