    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, that makes sense. a few days shouldn't hurt. by the way, i saw some old antihistamine eye drops in my cabinet from a few years ago, do you think it's okay if i use those instead of the lubricating ones to see if it helps the redness faster? might as well use what i have, right?",
